headline: Will U.S. WFE be exempted from China retaliatory tariffs?
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. wafer fab equipment (WFE) suppliers are unlikely to be exempt from China’s new 125% retaliatory tariffs, according to Bernstein analysts in a note Thursday.
